				<wikidot:authorName>DarkStuff</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1581620</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Honestly want to see the Foundation get utterly pummeled more often in these tales of yours. I felt like this was a perfect opportunity to have it be an indisputable loss, with some heroics thrown in there (such as Ferro calling Foundation protocol). But I do also understand that not everyone is as sadistic as I am, and the action here is real good. +1</p> 
				 	]]>
