					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-3592846#post-3589987</guid>
				<title>Another Edition of Site-64 Theater</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-3592846/assault-on-site-64#post-3589987</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Mon, 11 Sep 2017 22:55:51 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Jacob Conwell</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1372582</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Alright, so in creating this article I wanted to do something similar to what I did in <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/the-blackbird-and-the-falcon">The Blackbird and The Falcon</a>, in which there was a large piece with a lot of interconnecting pieces telling the story. The scenes are kept intentionally brief to amp up the pacing and make things snappy and fast. Obviously this time around, however, its the CI and the Foundation clashing rather than AR fighting off both the Foundation and the UIU.</p> <p>The decision to make Researcher Roland Ferro the most central character was due to him being someone whose made quite a few appearances in the background of my tales/articles so far, and being long overdue for characterization and his chance to shine in the spotlight.</p> <p>Arguably, this tale is far more akin to a summer blockbuster than a fall oscar-bait flik, but hey, it was really fun to write and I hope you have fun reading it.</p> <p>Special Thanks to the following for their review and critique: <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/taffeta" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2221240&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1505304686" alt="Taffeta" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2221240)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/taffeta" >Taffeta</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/minmin" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=560062&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1505304686" alt="minmin" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=560062)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/minmin" >minmin</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/roget" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1229263&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1505304686" alt="Roget" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1229263)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/roget" >Roget</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zyn" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1404533&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1505304686" alt="Zyn" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1404533)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zyn" >Zyn</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drmagnus" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=318209&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1505304686" alt="DrMagnus" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=318209)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drmagnus" >DrMagnus</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/modern-erasmus" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3129691&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1505304686" alt="Modern_Erasmus" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3129691)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/modern-erasmus" >Modern_Erasmus</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/waterfire" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1672816&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1505304686" alt="Waterfire" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1672816)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/waterfire" >Waterfire</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sunnyclockwork" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1621343&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1505304686" alt="SunnyClockwork" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1621343)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sunnyclockwork" >SunnyClockwork</a></span></p> <p>Lyrics are from the song Maps, by Yeah Yeah Yeahs</p> <p>Enjoy the tale.</p> <p><em>JC</em></p> 
				 	]]>
